<pb facs="1361319" n="1"/>
<opener>
<lb/>Viro Celeberrimo <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolao Bernoulli</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petrus Antonius Michelotti</rs>
</opener>
<p>
<lb/>Ut Te certiorem feci per <choice><abbr>Celeber.</abbr><expan>Celeberrimi</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patrui</rs>
<lb/>Tui <rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">Filium</rs> mihi carissimum de Tua electio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ne in <rs type="organisation">Professorem Matheseos Studii <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavini</rs></rs>,
              <lb/>non destiti Vir <abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">e</hi></abbr> id agere <add>ut </add>quamprimum
         <lb/>solemniter voceris ad docendum; idque felici
         <lb/>cum successu: etenim iam Tua dignissima
         <lb/>Persona proposita fuit <abbr>Excellentiss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr><del> Coleggio</del>
<lb/><rs type="organisation">Colegio</rs>, et brevi proponetur Serenissimo <rs type="organisation">Se<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>natui</rs>, a quo non dubito Te confirmatum iri.
         <lb/>Statim ac id pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stitum fuerit in Senatu (quod
              <lb/>ut cito pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stetur summa ope nitentur <abbr>Nobiliss.<hi rend="sup">i</hi></abbr>
      <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-1253768439 pers_DE-588-1178380696 pers_DE-588-1089924410" type="persons">Moderatores</rs> Fautores nostri <abbr>Generosiss.<hi rend="sup">i</hi></abbr>) solem<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nibus litteris vocaberis ut possis Tuas inchoare
         <lb/>Lectiones mense Novembris proximo. Vocaberis
         <lb/>autem procul dubio eodem salario, iisdemque
             <lb/>honoribus quibus stipatus et cumulatus fuit Ami<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cissimus <rs key="pers_DE-588-119112450" type="person">Hermannus</rs> vester; ego <choice><abbr>v.<hi rend="sup"><choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice></hi></abbr><expan>vero</expan></choice> minime
         <lb/>ambigo quin Tu gloriam, honorem, ac decus
             <lb/><rs type="organisation">Archilycei <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavini</rs></rs> Mathesin docendo sis auctu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rus.
      </p>
<p>
<lb/><del>Interim </del>Te admonebo de <choice><abbr>oibus</abbr><expan>omnibus</expan></choice> iis, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Tibi facienda
      <lb/>erunt erga <abbr>Excell.<hi rend="sup">os</hi></abbr> <abbr>D. D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1253768439 pers_DE-588-1178380696 pers_DE-588-1089924410" type="persons">Moderatores</rs> quum Te solem<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>niter vocabunt. Interim rogo ut transmittas
         <pb facs="1361320" n="2"/>
      <lb/>sine mora qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> addenda, et notanda habes ad <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_P88RGPV8">solutio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nem</rs> Tui <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_IMQW7IQZ">problema<unclear>t</unclear>is</rs> quam dedit <rs key="pers_DE-588-1156361761" type="person">Checozzi</rs>. Ete<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nim sub nomine <rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">Filii</rs> <choice><abbr>Celeber.</abbr><expan>Celeberrimi</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patrui</rs> Tui
      <lb/>ut inseratur <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_CB34DHV9">Tomo</rs> vigesimo quinto nostri
      <lb/><rs type="keyword">Diarii</rs> nitar siquidem <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_CB34DHV9">Tomus</rs>vigesimus quartus
      <lb/>in quo est <subst><del>t</del><add>T</add></subst>ua ultima <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_65T3BHVK">responsio</rs> ad <abbr>D.</abbr> Comitem
         <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-109091766X" type="person">Riccatum</rs> <add>iam</add> impressus est. Optimum hoc erit pro
         <lb/>ipso <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolao</rs>, qui ut etiam hic sibi famam
          <lb/>aquirat desidero. <abbr>D.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr> autem <rs key="pers_DE-588-1156361761" type="person">Checozzi</rs> est <abbr>Clariss.</abbr>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-119112450" type="person">Hermanni</rs> discipulus, iuvenis, et quidem talis
         <lb/>qui fortasse omnia qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> scripsit de Tuo proble<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mate, accepit ab ipso eximio <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119112450" type="person">Hermanno</rs>; id
      <lb/>quod mecum censet etiam <rs key="pers_DE-588-117596027" type="person">Zendrinus</rs>.
      </p>
<p>
<lb/>Si tempus Tibi est<del> omnia</del> confice qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>so huius
          <lb/>theorematis a <rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person">Newtono</rs> in <rs key="biblio_KGWAEINJ" type="biblio">Optica</rs> suppositi
         <lb/>(<abbr>pag.</abbr> <choice><abbr>m.</abbr><expan>mea</expan></choice><del> 2<unclear>91</unclear></del> 231<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>) demonstrationem.
      </p>
<p>
<lb/><add>Si </add>Corpus vel res qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cunque, interea dum movetur per
         <lb/>spatium dat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> latitudinis duobusque planis inter
         <lb/>se parallelis utrinque terminatum, urgeatur
         <lb/>prorsum in <choice><abbr>oibus</abbr><expan>omnibus</expan></choice> partibus istius spatii, viri<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bus directo versus posterius planum tendenti<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bus; et antequam incideret in prius planum, motu
         <lb/>vel nullo, vel infinite parvo fuerit eo versus delatum;
         <lb/>sique vires in omnibus partibus istius spatii inter
         <lb/>bina plana iacentibus, sint in <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualibus quidem
         <pb facs="1361321" n="3"/>
<lb/>intervallis, maiores, vel minores secundum quam<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>libet datam proportionem; utique motus viri<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bus istis generatus in toto transitu corporis vel
         <lb/>rei antedict<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> erit in subduplicata proportione
          <lb/>virium, ut Mathematici facile quidem
          <lb/>intelligent. <hi rend="u">Sunt <rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person">Newtoni</rs> verba.</hi></p>
<closer><lb/><salute><abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">um</hi></abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruum</rs> Tuum a me pluri<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mum salutatum cupio. Vale Vir Amicissi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>me, meque Tibi amicitia in perpetuum fore
         <lb/><del><unclear>devinctum et </unclear></del>coniunctissimu<unclear>m</unclear> <add>ac</add> paratum ad
      <lb/>Tibi inserviendum certus esto.</salute> <dateline>Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Ve<unclear>ne</unclear><note type="internal">ToDo: Hier soll noch geklärt werden, wie mit Textverlust (Text ist nicht mehr lesbar) und die ergänzende Konkektur umgegangen werden soll (Supplied, gap, unclear)</note> <pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tiis</rs> <date when="1716-06-19">19 Junii 1716</date>.</dateline></closer>
<postscript>
<p>
<lb/><abbr>P. S.</abbr> <abbr>D.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolaus</rs> Tuus consanguineus opti<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>me valet, Teque cum <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patre</rs> suo, totaque fami<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lia salutat.
         </p>
</postscript>
